  "instructions": [
    "Drain and rinse the refried beans, then warm them gently in a small saucepan or microwave until steaming hot, about 3 minutes.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the warmed beans, diced pickles, and crushed chickpeas.",
    "Whisk together olive oil, apple cider vinegar, lemon juice, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper until emulsified, then pour the dressing over the beans and toss to coat evenly.",
    "Fold in chopped parsley and adjust seasoning with additional salt or pepper if needed.",
    "Serve immediately with a side of crisp rye bread or as a light lunch on its own."
